---
title: Carb Smart Sheet Pan Chicken with Chickpeas and Veggies
description: This dinner is inspired by the flavours of summer in Tuscany! Tender chicken is smothered in pesto and served on top of chickpeas and zucchini. A drizzle of balsamic glaze adds a sweet-savoury finishing touch.

